l is to develop a great guild of friends to enjoy this game and later make planes and dragon raids.  We are like many of the guilds on this board and are only 35 to 40 strong at this point.  Our leader is Thinnok D'solar and he is a level forty paladin and our only other level forty is Estro another paladin.  We always welcome comraderie with other guilds and I have personally made many friends in some of your guilds already such as Avenging Crusaders, Sign of One and Silver Daggers just to name a few.  We have great respect for the guilds on karana and our main rules are typical such as no ninja looting, camp stealing, kill  stealing, etc.  We hope to have at least ten members ready to join the council for planes and dragon raids in a month or so or maybe two months.  We are accepting very few members under twenty five or thirty as this is where most of our members are at right now.  We also have group raids, wars, etc. every sunday to help prepare us for future large raids.  I think this will help us alot.  Our leader thinnok has actually played from day one and has been on planes and dragon raids.  This is very helpful and he is enjoying teaching many of us techniques.  He retired a forty nine paladin to take up his character now.  He has been there and done most of that on this game so he should be able to help the organizers of the planes raids in our council when he makes forty six or above again.  Again I would like to say thank you for having us and we look forward to our first guild war with the Silver Daggers next sunday.<br>
<br>
